OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FLorry driver shortage:     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FGovernment working on      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Ftemporary visa scheme      
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Details of a temporary visa scheme to  
OL,6, make it easier for foreign lorry       
OL,7, drivers to work in the UK are to be set
OL,8, out on Sunday.                         
OL,10,FAny changes to immigration rules would 
OL,11,Fbe for a limited period only, and there
OL,12,Fwould be a cap on the number of workers
OL,13,Fallowed to enter the country.          
OL,15,FIt is understood that about 5,000      
OL,16,Ftemporary visas could be issued.       
OL,18,FA shortage of drivers has disrupted    
OL,19,Ffuel deliveries, with some petrol      
OL,20,Fstations closing, and queues forming.  
